     <m:mi mathvariant="bold"> P </m:mi>
     <m:mo> + </m:mo>
     <m:mi mathvariant="bold"> Q </m:mi>
     </m:mtd>
   </m:mtr>
</m:mtable>
</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-34">
In order to determine the magnitude, we drop a perpendicular BC on the extended line OC. 
</para>
<para id="element-34a">
<figure id="fig34a"><title> Analytical method </title>
<media id="idm6352256" alt=""><image src="../../media/va6.gif" mime-type="image/gif"/></media>

</figure>
</para>
<para id="element-35">
In ∆ACB, 
</para>
