<para id="element-40">
Let "α" be the angle that line OA makes with OC, then
</para>
<para id="element-41">
<m:math display="block">
<m:mstyle displaystyle="true">
<m:mtable columnalign="left">
   <m:mtr>
     <m:mtd>
     <m:mi> tan </m:mi>
