<para id="element-382a">
<exercise id="exercise-382a">
<problem id="idm4775744">
<para id="element-383"> Two forces of 10 N and 25 N are applied on a body. Find the magnitude of maximum and minimum resultant force.
</para>
</problem>

<solution id="idm1114544">
<para id="element-384">  Resultant force is maximum when force vectors act along the same direction. The magnitude of resultant force under this condition is :
</para>
<para id="element-385">
